  "edge_hypothesis": "Cross-family synergy test: Supertrend direction flips (2 ACCEPTs in family, up to PF=1.921) are powerful trend-change signals but generate false signals during consolidation. Ichimoku cloud position (ISA_9) acts as a regime gate — only take Supertrend signals when price is on the correct side of the Ichimoku leading span. This combines two independently proven ACCEPT mechanisms: Supertrend trend-following (PF=1.907-1.921) and Ichimoku median-price transition detection (PF=1.604). Hypothesis: combining two proven families into one strategy creates a higher-quality signal filter, reducing false positives and improving profit factor above either family alone.",
